nodes.documentation: We need and ExtensionLib and an AdvancedExtensionLib because the IteratorLib builds upon the ExtensionLib and the AdvancedExtension needs the IteratorLib. Moving this function into ExtensionLib would lead to a cyclic dependency between ExtensionLib and IteratorLib.
